episodes.title: Derren Brown - The Heist | FULL EPISODE
episodes.description:
#DerrenBrown #Illusionist #TheHeist  

In this one off special Derren Brown recruits participants to attend a "motivational seminar" where he manipulates them into stealing £100,000 in what they believe is a genuine armed robbery of a bank's security guard (using a realistic-looking toy gun).

For more subscribe to our channel - 

http://www.youtube.com/user/OfficialDerren
